title: 请问为什么用了MCedit后就会出现错误讯息呢?
author: anasxwing
txt_content:
我使用mcedit将A地图的建筑物移到B地图，结果不知道为什么只要有人登入或是作某些事的时候就会出现以下的错误讯息

10:12:46 [WARNING] Wrong location for EntityItemFrame['entity.ItemFrame.name'/223, l='world', x=605.06, y=79.50, z=-250.50] in world 'world'!
10:12:46 [WARNING] Entity is at 605.0625,-250.5 (chunk 37,-16) but was stored in chunk 2,17
10:12:46 [WARNING] Wrong location for EntityItemFrame['entity.ItemFrame.name'/226, l='world', x=605.06, y=79.50, z=-252.50] in world 'world'!
10:12:46 [WARNING] Entity is at 605.0625,-252.5 (chunk 37,-16) but was stored in chunk 2,18


原本更长...但我只取其中两段(其实都差不多)，请问这是为什么呢? 以及这该怎么解决~? 谢谢

replies.author: Technology
replies.txt_content: 里面有没有不是原版生存里的东西？比如mod里面的东西？

replies.author: anasxwing
replies.txt_content:
Technology 发表于 2012-12-12 11:53

没有耶~我是用bukkit的服务器，所以没装任何MOD
